Text: MS Illinois Team Enron ThanksJeff Thanks again for yours and Enrons support of our ride Our MS Ride was this past weekend We had riders and volunteers Our ride is not as big as Houstons ride there was a rough total of riders and our team was the th largest with the top team having riders All riders finished with minimal mishaps and no SAGs We are still awaiting our fundraising totals Here is a copy of our Team photo Thanks once again for your support Sincerely Ron Girard Team Enron Midwest
